<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">يَقُولُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَبْلِغَنْ أَهْلَنَا وَلَا تُخْفِ عَنْهُمْ … مَا لَقِينَا فِي الْبَرْزَخِ الْخَنَّاقِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَدْ سُئِلْنَا عَنْ كُلِّ مَا قَدْ فَعَلْنَا … فَارْحَمُوا وَحْشَتِي وَمَا قَدْ أُلَاقِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">ثُمَّ قَالَ:</span> أَفَهِمْتَ؟<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> نَعَمْ.<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَلَوْ أَنَّا إِذَا مِتْنَا تُرِكْنَا … لَكَانَ الْمَوْتُ رَاحَةَ كُلِّ حَيِّ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلَكِنَّا إِذَا مِتْنَا بُعِثْنَا … وَنُسْأَلُ بَعْدَهُ عَنْ كُلِّ شَيِّ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ثُمَّ قَالَ:</span> أَفَهِمْتَ؟<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> نَعَمْ. وَانْتَبَهْتُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>